---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="CCPA / CPRA privacy readiness for technology companies. Protect consumer privacy and meet California's requirements.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="CCPA / CPRA Privacy Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Protect consumer privacy. Meet California's requirements. Build trust with data-conscious customers."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why CCPA / CPRA Matters</h2>
    <p>California's privacy laws set the standard for consumer data protection in the United States. Companies that handle California residents' personal information face direct regulatory scrutiny, litigation exposure, and competitive pressure to demonstrate privacy maturity.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Meet California Privacy Requirements</h3>
        <p>CCPA/CPRA are the strictest state privacy laws in the United States. Compliance is mandatory for businesses meeting revenue, data-volume, or data-sale thresholds that collect California residents' personal information.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Build Consumer Trust</h3>
        <p>Demonstrate commitment to data privacy through transparent practices, responsive consumer rights fulfillment, and clear privacy notices that build long-term customer relationships.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Reduce Litigation Risk</h3>
        <p>CCPA's private right of action for data breaches creates direct financial liability. Proactive compliance with security and privacy requirements reduces exposure to costly lawsuits.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Enterprise Privacy Maturity</h3>
        <p>A strong CCPA/CPRA posture signals privacy maturity to enterprise partners, investors, and customers &mdash; differentiating your organization in competitive markets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your compliance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Remediation Program</h3>
        <p>Close gaps and build your evidence machine</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Audit Support</h3>
        <p>Expert coordination during audit fieldwork</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Continuous Compliance</h3>
        <p>Stay audit-ready year-round</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're building a California privacy program from scratch or strengthening existing practices, we can help you map your data, implement consumer rights, and stay ahead of enforcement.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
